Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:14.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm so sick of eating this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:14.24,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,流石に飽きたぜ こういう飯ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.89,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Don't know how you can eat \Nit without complaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.89,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,文句も言わず よく食うな お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.88,Default,av,0,0,0,,You'll get hungry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.88,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,後で腹へるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:35.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,A truce with the Orcos?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:35.43,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,オルコと手打ち?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.25,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.25,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.66,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Orco finally made a move to snuff out Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.66,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,オルコは愈々 ファンゴを消しに動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:43.72,Default,bar,0,0,0,,But he failed, like we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:43.72,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,だが うちらと同じでやり損なった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.69,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あいつ等も両方を相手にできねぇから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:49.23,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And they can't afford to fight on both \Nfronts, either, so they want a truce?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.23,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ここで手打ちってか?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.27,Default,bar,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.27,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,まぁ そんなところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:54.34,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ファンゴは今 20人程掻き集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:56.26,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Fango got twenty or so guys together \Nand holed up on the Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.14,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アイランドを根城にしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.81,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アイランド?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:00.64,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Apparently he's connected \Nwith the owner, Granchio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:00.64,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,オーナーのグランキオと繋がっていたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.34,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's got his bases covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.34,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,しっかりしてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.88,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we can come home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.88,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まぁ やっと帰れるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.16,Default,bar,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.16,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,いや...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:08.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:08.43,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.32,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,うちとオルコが手打ちすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.47,Default,nero,0,0,0,,If we're making peace with the Orcos, \Nthe Galassias shouldn't have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:12.47,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ガラッシアも文句ねぇだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:15.81,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Yeah, Frate persuaded Ronaldo of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:15.81,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,あぁ ロナルドはフラテが説得した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.17,Default,bar,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.17,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,だが...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:21.84,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Could we meet up before you get into town?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:21.84,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,町に入る前に 少し会えないか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.37,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm in Portline now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.37,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今ポートラインだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.77,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Let's meet at the Lodge in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,明後日辺り ロッチでおちあう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:30.45,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:04.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,When we get back, do you \Nwant to join the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:04.31,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前 帰ったら ファミリーに入らねか
