Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.13,Default,av,0,0,0,,Are we continuing into the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.13,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,このまま町に入るのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.24,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's gonna get bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ちょっと揺れるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.52,Default,av,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.52,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,どこに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.68,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You'll see when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.68,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,着いてのお楽しみだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.13,Default,nero,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.13,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,こっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.43,Default,man,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.43,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,誰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's me, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺だ ネロだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.65,Default,av,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.65,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ここは?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's a moonshine brewery I had specially made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺が特別に作らせた密造酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.21,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I call it the Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.21,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ロッチって呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.46,Default,av,0,0,0,,It's a pretty big operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.46,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,随分盛大にやってるな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:24.26,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, I make some pretty good money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:24.26,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あぁ たんまり稼々でもらってね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.09,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.09,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.64,Default,bar,0,0,0,,With his alcohol in particular, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.64,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,特に今は こいつの酒でな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:35.52,Default,av,0,0,0,,Corteo... What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:35.52,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオ 何故ここに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.39,Default,cor,0,0,0,,They... asked for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.39,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ちょっと 頼まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.50,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.50,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,おかえり ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.24,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おぉ ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.76,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.76,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,こいつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.65,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It's fetching a better price than our\Nimports from Canada right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.65,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,今じゃ カナダの輸入ものより いい値がついてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:55.60,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ただ こいつのレシピが複雑なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:57.96,Default,bar,0,0,0,,But his recipe is complicated, \Nso we haven't distributed much yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.96,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,まだ大して流せてないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.34,Default,bar,0,0,0,,How about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.34,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,そっちはどうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.05,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I heard you did a bit of monster slaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.05,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,仲良く化物退治したんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.92,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, he handled things pretty well,\Nother than the driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.92,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あぁ 運転以外なら まぁまぁ役に立った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.31,Default,av,0,0,0,,I saved your life multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.31,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何回か命を救ってやっただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.61,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You can run your mouth after you \Npay me back for crashing the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.61,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,それはぶつけた車の代金を払ってから言えって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,Your booze really is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.74,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,やっぱりお前の酒が一番だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.52,Default,cor,0,0,0,,When will you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.52,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,いつやるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.28,Default,av,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.28,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,やる?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.46,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Nero's one of your revenge targets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.46,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ネロも復讐の相手なんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.48,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.48,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.25,Default,av,0,0,0,,You thought my revenge was stupid before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.25,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,この間まで復讐なんて下らないって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.42,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ドン バネッティに近付くには
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:53.22,Default,av,0,0,0,,If I want to get close to Don Vanetti, \NI need to earn his trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.22,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,まず奴の信用を得なきゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.84,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'll figure it out after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.84,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,話はそれからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.64,Default,av,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.83,Default,av,0,0,0,,You started smoking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.83,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,吸い始めたのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Avilio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.85,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:13.96,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Come with me! You want to \Njoin the family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:13.96,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,一緒に来い ファミリーに入りたいんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.12,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to Don Vanetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.12,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,合わせてやろう ドン バネッティに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:23.75,Default,av,0,0,0,,It might not be long before I kill him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:23.75,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そんなに遠くないかもな 奴をやるのも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.62,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,とにかく 屋敷へ戻っても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:28.61,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Anyway, once we're back at the mansion, \Ndon't take your eyes off Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.61,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ロナルドだけは目を離すな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I know. You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,分かってる 心配し過ぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.01,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Hey, Tigre. Is Nero in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.01,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,や ティグレ 兄さんはまだかい?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.24,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.24,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,まだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:58.72,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Frate, are you sure we can trust Orco?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:58.72,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,フラテ 本当にオルコを信じていいのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.40,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,あぁ 色々と面倒だったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:02.95,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Yeah, it took a whole lot of effort, \Nbut we worked out a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.12,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,手打ちは上手くいった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.30,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Oh, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.30,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,あっ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.00,Default,fra,0,0,0,,It's a little early, but why \Nnot come in for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.00,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,少し早いが 中で一杯どうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.07,Default,fra,0,0,0,,We can celebrate my brother's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.07,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんの帰還祝いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.20,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Is it any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.20,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,うまいのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.01,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Better than the stuff Nero's making on the sly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.01,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんがこそこそ作ってる酒よりな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:28.24,Default,or,0,0,0,,Even a pig wouldn't eat that slop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:28.24,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,あんなもんっは豚も食わねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:33.15,Default,or,0,0,0,,I told you, lasagna lives or \Ndies by the béchamel sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:33.15,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,ラザニアはベシャメルソースが命だつってるだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.80,Default,or,0,0,0,,Tell the chef...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.80,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,シェフに言っとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.70,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,今度まずい飯食わせやがったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:39.86,Default,or,0,0,0,,Next time he feeds me slop like this,\NI'm feeding {\i1}him{\i0} to the pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.18,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,てめぇを豚に食わせるとな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.04,Default,av,0,0,0,,That fat cow is Orco?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.04,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あのデブがオルコか?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.84,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.33,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,手打ちをした割には 物々しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Pretty well-guarded for a guy \Nwe've got a truce with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.82,Default,man,0,0,0,,Mr. Nero, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.82,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ネロさん お帰りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.98,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Where's Tigre?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.98,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ティグレはどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.50,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Inside the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.50,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,屋敷の中です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.39,Default,man,0,0,0,,He's having a drink with Frate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.39,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,フラテさんと飲んでますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.52,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,しょうがないな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.74,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:29.05,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Those aren't the usual guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:29.05,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,見張りの当番が変更されてる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.01,Default,man,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.48,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,待って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.94,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Open your door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.94,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そっちを開けとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Tigre!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.75,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ティグレ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.09,Default,av,0,0,0,,Okay, gun it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.09,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,よし 出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.59,Default,av,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.59,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,どうなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.36,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Like I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.66,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,知るか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.13,Default,man,0,0,0,,No hard feelings, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.42,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,悪く思わないでくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.03,Default,vor,0,0,0,,Tigre, keep the pressure on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.03,通用720日文-ja,vor,0,0,0,,ティグレ しっかり抑えてろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.98,Default,vor,0,0,0,,He's bleeding hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.98,通用720日文-ja,vor,0,0,0,,血が出過ぎだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.90,Default,vor,0,0,0,,We need to take him to a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.90,通用720日文-ja,vor,0,0,0,,速く医者に見せねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.82,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Not possible now. They'll trace us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.82,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今はダメだ 足が付いちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.89,Default,av,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.89,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,こいつは?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:37.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Volpe. I had him watching Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:37.06,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ボルペだ ロナルドを見張れせてた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:41.08,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was actually Frate \Nwho made the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:41.08,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,すみません 実際に動いたのはフラテのほうでした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He probably had a hunch we were onto them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.29,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,向こうも薄々感づいてたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.57,Default,av,0,0,0,,What tipped you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.57,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なぜあの時気づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.79,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Tigre raised his right hand, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.79,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ティグレが右手をあげただろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.33,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That was the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.33,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そういう取り決めだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.23,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Because of that, I didn't end up filled with holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.23,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お陰で蜂の巣を免れたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.30,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ありがどうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.85,Default,gan,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.85,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,一体どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.35,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Frate, explain this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.35,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,フラテ 説明しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.26,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,オルコは手打ちの条件として
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:08.13,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Orco demanded Nero's life as one \Nof the conditions of the truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.13,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんの命を要求してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:12.38,Default,fra,0,0,0,,It was Nero who tried to kill \NFango in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:12.38,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,そもそも 兄さんがファンゴの命を狙ったんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.71,Default,fra,0,0,0,,so it's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.71,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.42,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Only natural?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.42,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,当然だと?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.11,Default,fra,0,0,0,,He's getting his just desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.11,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,やったんだからやり返される
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.05,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.05,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,なぜ私に言わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.84,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't kill him, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.84,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,父さには兄さんは殺さない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.74,Default,fra,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.74,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,だから僕が...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.08,Default,vin,0,0,0,,You're willing to kill your own brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.08,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,実の兄を殺すというのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.75,Default,fra,0,0,0,,If I don't, the Galassias won't stand for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.75,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,殺しなけりゃ ガラッシアは黙ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.75,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.75,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,どうだかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:38.58,Default,fra,0,0,0,,We've always done what \Nthey say and always will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:38.58,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,今までもこれからも ずっとやつらの言いなりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.32,Default,fra,0,0,0,,But in exchange, they protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.72,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,でも 代わりに守ってもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.64,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You know that too, don't you, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.64,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,父さんだって分かってるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.90,Default,vin,0,0,0,,We are not the Galassias' puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.90,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,俺達はガラッシアの人形じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.46,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.46,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,うるせいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.53,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Is insulting each other the \Nsign of a close-knit family?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.53,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,罵り合うだけ仲がいいのか悪いのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:05.13,Default,ron,0,0,0,,A father and son shouldn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:05.13,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,親子喧嘩は見っともないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.70,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:10.70,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:21.78,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:21.78,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.22,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I think the bleeding has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.22,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,何とか血は止まった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.17,Default,bar,0,0,0,,And the bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.17,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,弾は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Looks like it passed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,抜けたみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.55,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Change the bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.55,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,包帯を変えてやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:33.23,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Did Dad know what was \Ngoing to happen today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:33.23,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今日のことを親父は知ってたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.23,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.23,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,そこまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:39.30,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,しかし この間お前らを襲った化け物も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:41.64,Default,bar,0,0,0,,But the monster who attacked you was \Nprobably sent by Ronaldo and Frate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.64,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,多分 ロナルドとフラテだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:45.54,Default,av,0,0,0,,Orcos ahead of us, Vanettis behind us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:45.54,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,前にオルコ 後ろにバネッティ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.70,Default,av,0,0,0,,Is it time for us to head back on our trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.70,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いっそうまた 旅にでも出るか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.55,Default,bar,0,0,0,,No, all the roads out of \Ntown are blocked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.55,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,いや 町から出る道は 全て抑えられてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.66,Default,cor,0,0,0,,It looks like they're stopping all \Nthe boats at the bridges, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.66,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,船も全部 橋の下で止められてるみたいだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.05,Default,bar,0,0,0,,And it's only a matter of time \Nbefore they find us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.05,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ここも見つかるのは 時間の問題だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:08.18,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Frate here will run the Vanettis from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:08.18,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,今後バネッティを仕切るのはフラテだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:13.83,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, you're basically \Nleaving the town to the Orcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:13.83,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,それが嫌ならこの町はオルコに任せると言ってるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.14,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Damn you! Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.62,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,てめえ 何様のつもり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.19,Default,or,0,0,0,,Well, either way is fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.19,通用720日文-ja,or,0,0,0,,まあ どっちだって構わないんですがね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:28.28,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Ronaldo, is that the word from Don Galassia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:28.28,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ロナルド それはドン ガラッシアからか?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.90,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.90,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,他に誰が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:35.37,Default,ron,0,0,0,,And I have one other request for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:35.37,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,後 もう一つお願いがありましたね お父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.02,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Nero needs to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.02,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロには死んでもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.92,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Avilio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.92,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.38,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Hard to sleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.38,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,やっぱり寝づらいね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.98,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I miss my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.98,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ベッドが恋しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.79,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Avilio... Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.79,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ ここ出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.29,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.29,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:15.86,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Why? Because this had nothing \Nto do with us from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:15.86,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,なぜって もともと僕たちには関係ない話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.70,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオがやられなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:21.01,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Nero's going to be killed \Nwithout you doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:21.01,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ほっといたってネロは殺されてる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.92,Default,av,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.92,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だめだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.69,Default,av,0,0,0,,If we leave now, I'll never reach Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.69,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,今ここで離れたら ヴィンセントまで辿り着けない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:32.21,Default,av,0,0,0,,Plus, there's a fourth man \Nwho wasn't in the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:32.21,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,それに 手紙にはなかった4人目の男にも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.37,Default,cor,0,0,0,,If we stay here, we'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.37,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ここにいたら死ぬんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:38.06,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Isn't your life worth more\Nthan some revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:38.06,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,復讐なんかより 自分が生きることのほうが大事じゃないか?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.46,Default,av,0,0,0,,You've got it backwards, Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.46,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,逆なんだ コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.14,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,復讐をやめたら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:51.25,Default,av,0,0,0,,If I abandon my revenge, \NI lose my reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.25,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺は生きてる意味を失ってしまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.66,Default,nero,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.66,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.49,Default,vol,0,0,0,,He's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.49,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,気を失ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.47,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sorry, Tigre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.47,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,悪いなティグレ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.39,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I can't take you to a doctor right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.39,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今は医者に見せてやれねんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.51,Default,bar,0,0,0,,He might last another day, at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.51,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,もって 明日いっぱいがせいぜいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.11,Default,av,0,0,0,,There is a way to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.11,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,助ける方法がある
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:20.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:20.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうやって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.46,Default,av,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.46,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あそこさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.03,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.03,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アイランド?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.98,Default,av,0,0,0,,There are doctors there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.98,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あそこには医者もいるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.37,Default,av,0,0,0,,And they're hostile to the \NVanettis, who are chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.37,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺たちを追っているヴァネッティとも敵対している
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.50,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.50,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ふさげんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Fango's killed a bunch of our guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.08,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴには何人もやられた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And Vanno, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴだって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.91,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm working with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.91,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そんなやつと組めるわけねえだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.02,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.02,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:16:00.06,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Fango has no reason to take us in anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:16:00.06,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,そもそも ファンゴのほうに俺たちを受け入れる理由がない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.13,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I feel for Tigre, but our only hope is to \Nfind an opening and get to the Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.13,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ティグレには悪いな 隙を見てロッジに移るしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.13,Default,av,0,0,0,,Corteo, where's the booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.13,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオ酒は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.29,Default,cor,0,0,0,,In the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.29,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,車の中だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.31,Default,av,0,0,0,,Corteo, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.31,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオ一緒に来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.36,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'm going to escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.36,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺はここを抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.43,Default,cor,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.43,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,でもどうやって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.54,Default,av,0,0,0,,Let's cross it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.54,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,渡ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.62,Default,av,0,0,0,,The river of lamentation \Ninto the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.62,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,冥府に至る嘆きの川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.58,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Hey... You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.58,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,お おい お前らは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:07.43,Default,av,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:07.43,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,速く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.80,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,どこへいく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.81,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.95,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,戻ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.95,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.86,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.64,Default,man,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.64,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,何だお前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.81,Default,av,0,0,0,,We'd like to sell some alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.81,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,酒を買ってもらえたいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:44.12,Default,man,0,0,0,,Get lost. We don't want \Nyour crummy booze here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:44.12,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,帰れ お前らの酒をおく場所じゃねい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:45.72,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.04,Default,av,0,0,0,,That's what Mr. Granchio said at first, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.04,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,グランキオさんも最初そう言ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.40,Default,gran,0,0,0,,Hey. You made quite a scene here last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.40,通用720日文-ja,gran,0,0,0,,よ この間派手にやってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.22,Default,gran,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve, showing up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.22,通用720日文-ja,gran,0,0,0,,よく顔出せたもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.62,Default,gran,0,0,0,,Trying to sell your booze here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.62,通用720日文-ja,gran,0,0,0,,またこの酒を売りつけようってのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.06,Default,av,0,0,0,,No, it's an apology for the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.06,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いや 火事のお詫びだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.16,Default,av,0,0,0,,The rest is on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.16,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,残りはボードに積んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.95,Default,gran,0,0,0,,I'll take it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.95,通用720日文-ja,gran,0,0,0,,なら 遠慮なく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.12,Default,av,0,0,0,,I want to see Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.12,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ファンゴに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.51,Default,gran,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.51,通用720日文-ja,gran,0,0,0,,何の用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:27.30,Default,av,0,0,0,,That's for him to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:27.44,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,それは本人に話す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.35,Default,gran,0,0,0,,Get lost. Mr. Fango would \Nnever do business with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.35,通用720日文-ja,gran,0,0,0,,帰りな ファンゴさんはお前見たいな...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.20,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.52,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,いらっしゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:33.77,Default,lac,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:33.77,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,こっち
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.13,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Cerotto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.13,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,チェロット
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:47.85,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:47.85,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:52.19,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I betrayed Mr. Scusa thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:52.19,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,お前らのおかけでスクーザの旦那を裏切っちまっただからな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.60,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,もう町を出歩けねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:57.06,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Now I can't show my face around town, \Nso I'm here working for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.06,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,だからここでただ働きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.42,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.42,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,速くなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.74,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Mr. Fango's even crazier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.74,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ファンゴさんは思ったより いかれてる人だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.13,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You damn sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.13,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,このメス豚よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.13,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You just can't stop bringing in the young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.13,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,若いのぞろぞろ連れ込みやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.80,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Thinking about a foursome today, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.80,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,じゃ 今日は四人でやるってのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.70,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can hold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.80,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺が持たねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.09,Default,lac,0,0,0,,I just brought them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.09,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,私は連れてきただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.39,Default,lac,0,0,0,,If you're up to it, it'll just \Nbe the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.39,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,やるなら三人でどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.72,Default,lac,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.72,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,後でね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.59,Default,lac,0,0,0,,That is, assuming you make \Nit out of this room alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.59,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,生きてこの部屋から出られたら だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.77,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.44,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You're making me jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.44,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,妬けるじゃねぇかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.45,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.45,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,んだよ お前らか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.94,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そういや ネロは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:48.77,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That's right. I hear the Orcos and \NVanettis are chasing Nero all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:48.77,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,オルコとバネッティから追い回されてるそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.82,Default,av,0,0,0,,We want you to hide us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.82,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,匿ってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.26,Default,av,0,0,0,,We have a wounded man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.26,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,怪我人もいる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.75,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I like it! What a funny joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.75,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,いいね おもしれぇジョークだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.77,Default,av,0,0,0,,You have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.77,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そっちにも損はないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.85,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Nothing to lose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.85,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,損がねぇだと?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:09.14,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Nero and his gang took out Serpente...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:09.14,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺はネロたちにセルペンテを殺された
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:13.66,Default,fan,0,0,0,,He used to trim my beard with his knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:13.66,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ナイフで髭をよく剃ってくれたんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.83,Default,fan,0,0,0,,When I think about how much I miss him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.83,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,彼奴の胸を思うと...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.48,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I know that I can never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.48,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺はお前を絶対許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:31.09,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. I'm not that type.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:31.09,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ってまぁ タイプじゃねぇけどな 確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.35,Default,fan,0,0,0,,So? You got anything good to offer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.35,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,で 俺になんかいいことあんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.87,Default,vol,0,0,0,,They betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.87,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,彼奴ら裏切りやがったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.59,Default,vol,0,0,0,,They're gonna sell us to Fango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.59,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,俺たちをファンゴに売るつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.80,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,いや それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:46.73,Default,bar,0,0,0,,No, if he were going to sell us out, \Nhe'd choose Orco or Vanetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.73,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,オルコかバネッティを選ぶはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.06,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Then why—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.06,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,じゃなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.81,Default,cor,0,0,0,,He didn't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.81,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,裏切ったんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.14,Default,vol,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.14,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,お前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.17,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Where's Avilio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.17,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アヴィリオは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.21,Default,cor,0,0,0,,He's Fango's hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.21,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ファンゴの人質になってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.40,Default,cro,0,0,0,,I have a message from Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.40,通用720日文-ja,cro,0,0,0,,アヴィリオから伝言だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.70,Default,cor,0,0,0,,"Bring Tigre and come to the Island."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.70,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ティグレをつれてアイランドへ来い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.80,Default,cor,0,0,0,,"I'll negotiate with Fango."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.80,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ファンゴとは話をつけておく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.19,Default,vol,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.19,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.76,Default,cor,0,0,0,,If we stay here, Tigre will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.76,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ここに居続ければ ティグレは死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.31,Default,cor,0,0,0,,And so will you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.31,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,そして あんたたちも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.42,Default,cor,0,0,0,,So the Island is the only place you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.42,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,だから アイランドへ行くしか道はない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.12,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof this isn't a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.12,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,罠じゃないという証拠は?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:21.11,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'm going to be your hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:21.11,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕があんた達の人質になる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.89,Default,vol,0,0,0,,You think we can trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.89,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,そんなこと信用できるかよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.57,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We can trust Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.57,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アヴィリオは信じていい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.72,Default,nero,0,0,0,,But we can't trust Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.72,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,だがな ファンゴは信用できねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:33.46,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's entirely possible he'll \Nbetray us and kill us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:33.46,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺たちを騙して皆殺しってこともありうる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.97,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Of course, it comes with conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.97,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,勿論条件付きさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:40.14,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You got anything good to offer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:40.14,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺になんかいいことあんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.41,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'll bring Don Orco to you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.41,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ドン オルコを生きたまま連れてきてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.51,Default,av,0,0,0,,You can do what you want with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.51,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,好きに料理すればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.25,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Orco?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.25,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,オルコ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.69,Default,av,0,0,0,,You want to take over his family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.69,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,奴のファミリーを乗っ取りたいんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.49,Default,av,0,0,0,,You can't do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.49,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんたじゃ無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:55.19,Default,av,0,0,0,,The twenty men you have here aren't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:55.19,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ここに引っ張って来た20人ばかしじゃ 数が足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.88,Default,av,0,0,0,,They don't seem to like you much, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.88,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,人望もなさそうだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:02.85,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:02.85,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.87,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You do get under my skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.87,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,いらつく野郎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.26,Default,fan,0,0,0,,So, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.26,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,で どうやんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:09.04,Default,av,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:09.04,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,さぁな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.85,Default,fan,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.85,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,This was Nero's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.02,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,これはネロのアイデアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.17,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:16.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I don't have any ideas for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:16.31,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そんなアイデアどこにもねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.04,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.04,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,あるかないかは問題じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.88,Default,bar,0,0,0,,If you let him think you do, \NFango won't attack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.88,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,あると思わせて置けば ファンゴは手を出してこない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:25.54,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:25.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:29.90,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm the one who said I didn't \Nwant to work with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:29.90,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そもそも彼奴と組みたくねぇっつってんのは俺なんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:36.21,Default,cor,0,0,0,,B-But... Avilio said you weren't \Nthe type to just let a friend die...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:36.21,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,でも アヴィリオがあんたは仲間を見殺しにする奴じゃないって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:46.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:46.58,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:51.98,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,てめぇから嘆きの川を渡るとは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:53.79,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There's something wrong about you crossing \Nthe river of lamentation before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:53.79,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうかしてるぜ
